        "TileImage": "$($repository 7d79859c-7b10-4978-8387-199526dc6220).Image",
        "Description": "Dr Paine has infected multiple other militia members with the Nabazov virus, in hopes of researching transmission rates and examining specific strains to concoct the most potent one himself. This virus must not be allowed to spread outside of the compound, and definitely needs to be contained at all costs. Eliminate these targets and anybody they spend time with to maike sure the virus is not able to spread to the outside world.",
